GO analysis

go <- msigdbr::msigdbr("Mus musculus", "C5")
go <- go[which(go$gs_subcat == "BP"), ]
go <- split(go$gene_symbol, go$gs_name)

goc <- goclassify(list, go)

  plot.goclassify(goc,
    row_names_gp = gpar(fontsize = 10),
    column_names_gp = gpar(fontsize = 10),
    cluster_columns = TRUE,
    cluster_rows = TRUE,
